Build a fully working E-Commerce Website with the following requirements:

✅ Project Requirements

Main Features:

Users should be able to:

Explore products (products list page)

View product details (single product page)

Add products to shopping cart

View and manage cart items (increase, decrease, remove)

Website Requirements:

Clean, modern, responsive UI

Frontend must use:

React.js (or Next.js, but prefer React.js)

React Router for navigation

State management for cart (Context API preferred)

Backend Requirements:

Node.js with Express.js

REST APIs:

GET /products

GET /products/:id

POST /cart/add

DELETE /cart/remove/:id

Database:

MongoDB Atlas

Create “products” collection with sample data

